lead_paragraph: Federal authorities have lodged two criminal charges against a Phoenix woman accused of throwing a shoe at Hillary Rodham Clinton while she gave a convention speech at a Las Vegas Strip resort.

headline.main: Feds Charge Woman in Hillary Clinton Shoe-Throw
